                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>106000</citedRange></bibl>. 
                    Cf. <bibl> <ptr target="#masson1965a"/>, pp. <citedRange>238-239</citedRange></bibl> and
                    <bibl> <ptr target="#fraser-matthews1987"/>, p. <citedRange>96</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
